author: GameSpot
description:
Resident Evil Requiem is launching with path tracing and NVIDIA DLSS 4 with Multi Frame Generation on February 27th, 2026.

Resident Evil Requiem is the highly anticipated ninth title in the mainline Resident Evil series. Prepare to escape death in a heart-stopping experience that will chill you to your core.

#nvidia #residentevilrequiem #residentevil9
title: Resident Evil Requiem | 4K Path Tracing & NVIDIA DLSS 4 Trailer

author: GameSpot
description:
Begin the adventure that crosses seas and transcends time!
Play the free demo for DRAGON QUEST VII Reimagined starting January 7th and carry over your progress into the full game when it releases on February 5, 2026.

Adventures who have demo saved data on their console and continue their journey in the full game will also receive a reward - Maribel's "Day Off Dress".

Play the free demo when it comes to Nintendo Switch 2, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and Steam. 

#dragonquest #dragonquest7 #videogames
title: DRAGON QUEST VII Reimagined - Official Opening Movie Cinematic Trailer
